It also returns
.code t
for these additional characters:
.codn #\exa0 ,
.codn #\ex1680 ,
.codn #\ex180e ,
.codn #\ex2000 ,
.codn #\ex2001 ,
.codn #\ex2002 ,
.codn #\ex2003 ,
.codn #\ex2004 ,
.codn #\ex2005 ,
