.synb
.mets (span-str < str << set )
.syne
.desc
The
.code span-str
function determines the longest prefix of string
.meta str
which
consists only of the characters in string
.metn set ,
in any combination.

.coNP Function @ compl-span-str
.synb
.mets (compl-span-str < str << set )
.syne
